text.section:
The State Archivist shall provide, without charge:
to the State Law Library, 25 cloth-bound copies of each new Maryland Manual;
to each member of the General Assembly, 2 cloth-bound copies and 8 other copies of each new Maryland Manual;
to each public or private educational institution in the State, 1 copy of each new Maryland Manual; and
to the Legislative Library, 50 cloth-bound copies of each new Maryland Manual.
